version_description:
- Fixed issue related to showing playback controls on lockscreen when UDP is used;
- Fixed issues with DTMF keypad;
- Possible fix for losing registration on UDP.
- Various fixes for crashes on iOS 9.

- Various performance improvements;
- Improved reverse lookup on call log screen;
- Improved reverse lookup on chat;
- Fixed issue with the video reinvite;
- Fixed issue with ringtones per account; 
- Fixed issue with magnifier icon overlapping the text in the Search field;
- Fixed issue with playback appearing on the lockscreen;
- Fixed issue with Zoiper overtaking the playback controls on the Control panel;
- Fixed issue with stripping characters on call transfer;
- Fixed issue with multiple showing of the TLS certificate alert;

- Added SRTP support;
- Added new GUI controls during video calls;
- Added an option to automatically enable speaker on video calls;
- Added ability to make blind call transfers to manually entered numbers;
- Changed default focus on new messages screen to be on the recipients field instead of the message box;
- Fixed issues where Zoiper is stopping the music player when opened;
- Fixed noise on the speaker which appears sometimes when Zoiper is in background;
- Fixed issues with not recorded numbers shown as unknown in the notifications;
- Fixed issues with entering long numbers which led to showing the number in exponential format;
- Fixed security indicator on the in-call screen;
- Fixes on the certificate validation when TLS is used;
- Fixes for various crashes;
- Fixes on the Spanish localization;
- Fixes on the Italian localization;
- Fixes on the VoIP provider lists;
- Possible fix for the issue with Zoiper not starting at all;
- Improved background handling for UDP accounts;
- Improvements on the GUI for the chat screen;
- Improvements on the Video calls;
- Possible improvements on the battery usage when UDP accounts are used;
- Various performance improvements;
- Various fixes and improvements;

- Added handling for media server restart;
- Fixed issue with lowering other applications audio when Zoiper is running;
- Fixed issue with locking the number rewriting settings when an account is added;
- Fixed issues with clicking noise;
- Fixed layout for IAX account settings;
- Fixed issues with Zoiper not stripping non-breakable spaces from the numbers;
- Fixed some crashes;
- Various fixes and stability improvements;

- Improved IPv6 and NAT64 support;
- GUI fixes;
- Fix for the crashes on startup on iOS 5.1 and iOS 6 versions;
- Various fixes and improvements;

- Audio improvements;
- Improved IPv6 support;
- Fixed crash on selected different DTMF type;
- Fixed crash when dialling with Zoiper protocol;
- Various fixes and improvements;

- Added push notifications;
- Added CallKit;
- Various fixes and improvements.

- Fixed rare crash on the start of the application;
- Fixed issue with the showing of the search field in the Contacts tab;
- Various fixes and improvements.

We follow our users feedback and are constantly trying to improve our application in the best way possible. In this version you will find:- fixes related to the push notifications and incoming calls;
- fixed layout of the search bar in contacts;
- fixes on screen transaction animations being performed twice;
- fixed bug in call history of the device with CallKit, the number is shown under 'Social profile' of the call record;
- fixed but in the chat where message input field is hidden bu the keyboard;
- fixes on the Number rewriting feature;
- fixed bug where call is put on 'Hold' when conference call is over;
- fixed ringtone selection;
- fixed custom ringtone not being applied for calls;
- fixed issue with Zoiper shown in wrong language when the device regional settings are changed;
- fixed crash on editing or deleting contacts within Zoiper;
- fixed rare crash on startup of the application;
- fixed crash on editing the account settings;
- improvements on the application stability;
- improvements related to dialling numbers with special characters in them;
- improvements on the reverse lookup for numbers;
- some improvements on the Bluetooth devices usage;
- various fixes and improvements.

We follow our users feedback and are constantly trying to improve our application in the best way possible. In this version you will find:
- fixed crash on making calls;
- fixed crash on enabling push notifications;
- stability improvements;
- various fixes and improvements.

- Fully re-implemented push notifications to conform  with requirements for iOS 13 and above;
- Fixed missing device token issue;
- Fixed dialing from system "Recents" tab;
- UI fixes and improvements;
- Various improvements and bug fixes.
